trans-unit.source: Specifies the default event for a component.
Use the <xref:System.ComponentModel.DefaultEventAttribute.Name%2A> property to get the name of the default event.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DefaultEventAttribute"></xref> class.
The name of the default event for the component this attribute is bound to.
